The primary bathroom is equipped with double sinks, ensuring convenience while getting ready. You'll also appreciate the good under sink storage, allowing for a clutter-free space. The fenced-in backyard provides privacy and security, while the covered sitting area offers a relaxing spot to enjoy the outdoors.
